✅ Approved the contribution.
Comment: Rapide à faire et plutôt sympa je trouve, c'est bien le genre de clash sur lequel je voudrais tomber

✅ Approved the contribution.
Comment: The fact that the description is written from the perspective of Tarzan but the distances are from the perspective of Jane is confusing. I would either phrase the start as "Can you help *Jane* figure out how far Tarzan will fall?" or just list the distances from Tarzan's perspective.

Other than that, this is good!

Also, this could be put in the shortest program category.

✅ Approved the contribution.
Comment: I enjoyed this one as a fastest task. For the reverse mode this seems a bit too specific IMO.
Let me know if you don't think this should be fastest and I might change it to reverse only. Also I'm sure it may have been done before so let me know.
i was worried about that too, i toggled reverse off.
